<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>النَّوْعُ الثَّانِي مِنْ أَنْوَاعِ الصَّلَاةِ <span class="c2">(صَلَاةُ اَلتَّطَوُّع)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> سُنَنٌ رَاتِبَةٌ مُرْتَبِطَةٌ بِالصَّلَوَاتِ اَلْخَمْس<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(راجع مبحث: الصَّلَوَات الْخَمْس)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> الصَّلَوَاتُ الْمَسْنُونَةُ الْمُطْلَقَة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> صَلَاةُ الْعِيدَيْنِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>حُكْمُ صَلَاةِ الْعِيدَيْنِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٢ص٢٣:</span> وَأَمَرَ أَنَسُ بْنُ مَالِكٍ مَوْلاَهُمْ ابْنَ أَبِي عُتْبَةَ بِالزَّاوِيَةِ فَجَمَعَ أَهْلَهُ وَبَنِيهِ، وَصَلَّى كَصَلاَةِ أَهْلِ المِصْرِ وَتَكْبِيرِهِمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>